snippet.title: Vomitoreum Kickstarter and Demo live now!
snippet.description:
Vomitoreum is an FPS metroidvania inspired by the artwork of Zdzisław Beksiński.

Play the demo:
https://scumhead.itch.io/vomitoreum
Support the kickstarter:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/scumhead/vomitoreum
